HEADWORD: Rocket scientist
<hw>Rock"et sci"en*tist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a very
intelligent person; -- used mostly in the phrases: ⟦ldquo⟧you don't have
to be a <ex>rocket scientist</ex> to . . .⟦rdquo⟧ and ⟦ldquo⟧it doesn't
take a <ex>rocket</ex> scientist to . . .⟦rdquo⟧, meaning that the
subject that follows is easy to understand.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

